156
00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:50,520
In your eyes, do I also deserve to die?

157
00:15:08,680 --> 00:15:12,760
Even if you ask so many questions, you have to die anyway.

158
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:15,700
But…

159
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:22,660
