167
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:52,460
I have to die anyway.

168
00:15:58,280 --> 00:16:02,340
I might as well drag Madam Shen down with me and use her as a scapegoat.

169
00:16:02,340 --> 00:16:04,440
I can plead for you.

170
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:06,720
He might leave you an intact body.

171
00:16:06,720 --> 00:16:09,540
We have a very good relationship.

172
00:16:09,540 --> 00:16:11,320
The whole Xiang'an City knows it well.

173
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:13,480
He will listen to me.

