 He will listen to me. 

177
00:16:21,800 --> 00:16:24,000
Shut up!

178
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:25,560
You shut up!

179
00:16:25,560 --> 00:16:27,160
You shameless hussy!

180
00:16:27,160 --> 00:16:28,440
He won't listen to you.

181
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:31,980
He is mine, mine, mine!

182
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,796
Stop.

183
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:42,316
Let me go!

184
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:46,008
Sixth Miss.

185
00:16:48,240 --> 00:16:50,200
Are you all right?

186
00:16:51,300 --> 00:16:53,000
Sixth Miss.

187
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:09,980
Thank you for arriving in time.

188
00:17:17,680 --> 00:17:20,440
Fortunately, you'd sprinkled flour on your clothes.

189
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:22,979
The dog could follow your scent over here.

190
00:17:32,480 --> 00:17:34,268
How do you feel?

191
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:38,400
I-I'm fine.

192
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:40,920
But…

193
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:43,040
Have you caught the murderer?

194
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:05,020
 But I had a dream. 

195
00:18:05,840 --> 00:18:07,584
Jing Lin.

196
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:12,540
Take off her mask.

197
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:24,012
