198
00:18:32,200 --> 00:18:33,988
Sixth Miss.

199
00:18:37,200 --> 00:18:39,440
Take her to the Imperial Guards.

200
00:18:39,440 --> 00:18:40,580
Yes.

201
00:18:40,580 --> 00:18:43,360
- Take her away. 
 - Yes.

202
00:19:05,400 --> 00:19:08,720
Sixth Miss, you're awake.

203
00:19:08,720 --> 00:19:13,480
Chuichui, how long have I slept?

204
00:19:14,720 --> 00:19:17,440
Where is Madam Tang? Has she been interrogated?

205
00:19:17,440 --> 00:19:19,520
You've only slept for two hours.

206
00:19:19,520 --> 00:19:22,640
Why are you asking these questions right after waking up?

207
00:19:23,800 --> 00:19:27,120
No wonder Shen Du asked me to keep a good eye on you.

208
00:19:27,120 --> 00:19:29,100
What's the outcome?

209
00:19:29,960 --> 00:19:32,880
Of course, she won't admit it.

210
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:36,420
But the Empress Dowager visits the Imperial Guards

211
00:19:36,420 --> 00:19:39,120
to interrogate her personally.

212
00:19:39,120 --> 00:19:41,600
Let's see if she will admit it this time.

213
00:19:41,600 --> 00:19:43,480
I'll go.

214
00:19:43,480 --> 00:19:45,640
You stay.

215
00:19:47,360 --> 00:19:50,160
You're not even off your medicine yet.

216
00:19:50,160 --> 00:19:52,080
I've been investigating this murderer for a long time.

217
00:19:52,080 --> 00:19:54,040
I know how to make her talk.

218
00:19:54,040 --> 00:19:55,720
No way.

219
00:19:55,720 --> 00:19:58,540
