356
00:29:56,240 --> 00:29:59,000
If it weren't for my momentary lapse in judgment...

357
00:29:59,000 --> 00:30:04,660
I wouldn't have lost both my loved ones at the same time.

358
00:30:04,660 --> 00:30:07,000
So, you regret it.

359
00:30:07,000 --> 00:30:12,460
You put those bodies in a hug pose to fulfill their wish.

360
00:30:12,460 --> 00:30:14,520
Madam Shen,

361
00:30:15,480 --> 00:30:18,200
